evidence.text: The Court GRANTS Petitioners’ preliminary injunction motion. In granting Petitioners’ motion, the Court presumes a reader’s familiarity with this case’s legal, factual, and procedural background set forth in the Court’s TRO order, as well as the Court’s May 6, 2025 order granting Petitioners’ Motion for Class Certification

The Court’s order remains in effect for no longer than fourteen (14) days, as the Court has set a hearing on this matter for April 21, 2025, and will promptly issue an order as to the motion for a TRO.
